Class EngineConfig

  • Object
    • EngineConfig

  • public class EngineConfig
extends Object
    This class provides an overview of Configs related to the game engine (a.k.a. BANG).
    Author
    Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com

      • renderIncreaseGamma

        public void renderIncreaseGamma(int amount)

      • renderDecreaseGamma

        public void renderDecreaseGamma(int amount)
